Actions.Text: REFERENCE CHANGED TO WAYS AND MEANS

Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to 9-11 Fallen Firefighters
Summary: Dedicates a portion of the Long Island Expressway in the town of Brookhaven to 9-11 Fallen Firefighters.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to dedicating a portion of the state highway system to 9-11 Fallen Firefighters
